flowchart LR
    Client([Sync Agent<br/>computes chunk hashes])
    PeerDevice([Peer Device])
    Metadata[Metadata Service]
    Block[Block Service]
    Notify[Notify Service<br/>WebSocket]
    MetaStore[(Transactional Store<br/>files, versions, ACLs)]
    Blobs[(Object Store<br/>content-addressed chunks)]

    Client -->|file meta + hashes| Metadata
    Metadata -->|missing chunks| Client
    Client -->|upload missing| Block
    Metadata --> MetaStore
    Block --> Blobs
    Metadata -.->|file_changed| Notify
    Notify -.->|WS push| PeerDevice
    PeerDevice -->|fetch metadata| Metadata
    PeerDevice -->|fetch chunks| Block

    classDef external fill:#1e2533,stroke:#3a4a6e,color:#cfd6e6
    classDef service fill:#1a3a2e,stroke:#3a6e54,color:#cfe6d6
    classDef store fill:#1e2a3e,stroke:#3a5a8e,color:#cfdcef
    classDef config fill:#3a2e1a,stroke:#6e5a3a,color:#efdfcf

    class Client,PeerDevice external
    class Metadata,Block,Notify service
    class MetaStore,Blobs store
